<#
.SYNOPSIS
    This PowerShell script tells Windows to record additional authentication-related activities that don’t fall into the basic logon/logoff categories such as: Special logon events (e.g., elevated privileges), Session reconnections/disconnections, and other authentication behaviors..

.NOTES
